   - Practical performance analysis and optimization
   - Very relevant for modern cloud/distributed systems
   - Great for understanding bottlenecks and optimization

These three books will give you the most value for your time and are all well-formatted for Kindle/iPad reading. Start with DDIA if you have to pick just one.
